<subSubSection id="A1850FEBFB6CDABC4C164A64086674E8" pageId="0" pageNumber="103" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="F91C6337D675FA99CD1F9E3AA5EFC565" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="774E00C6C14F94970AE128485C70FEB1" pageId="0" pageNumber="103">Named in honor of Fumitaka Ohashi (Aichi Prefecture, Japan) who collected and donated a large part of the studied otoliths and has undertaken an original thesis on the fossil contents of many of the locations covered in this study.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
